"{\"uid\": \"self.com-story-olympic-womens-gymnastics-team-paris-2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"If you were able to correctly choose all the members of the US women's Olympic gymnastics team before the Trials in June, well, you might want to go ahead and buy a lottery ticket right now.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9957419300604237, \"rank\": 0.004275026452897043, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the members\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 52}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trials\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"a lottery ticket\", \"from\": 163, \"to\": 179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's because the results were nearly impossible to predict, thanks to injuries that took several of the front-runners out of commission.\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 272}, {\"ngram\": \"the front-runners\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"commission\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heading into the Trials, it looked like the team had a couple of locks for the five available team spots-Simone Biles, of course, fresh off her historic ninth national all-around title and preparing for her third Olympics, being one of them.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Trials\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"locks\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"the five available team spots\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"her historic ninth national all-around title\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"her third Olympics\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two-time national uneven bars champShilese Jones, Tokyo alternate Kayla DiCello, and Skye Blakely all seemed like they could be likely contenders as well, along with, of course, Olympic veterans like Jordan Chiles and Jade Carey, who were looking to make it to their second Games.\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9421511614332093, \"rank\": 0.06140080374676294, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skye_Blakely\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skye Blakely\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skye_Blakely\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skye_Blakely\"}, {\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two-time national uneven bars\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"champShilese Jones\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"likely contenders\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"their second Games\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then in a three-day span before and during Trials, Blakely, Jones, and DiCello were all out of the running with serious injuries: Blakely and DiCello to their Achilles and Jones to her knee.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.83048533922977e-21, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a three-day span\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"Trials\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"DiCello\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"serious injuries\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"her knee\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When those gymnasts scratched from competition, what appeared to be a race for one, maybe two spots on the team suddenly opened up.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those gymnasts\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"two spots\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the time the Trials concluded on June 30-with Biles finishing in first place-the final team was one few would have predicted just a few days prior.\", \"fro