the \\\"twisties\\\"during her vault in the team competition at Tokyo Olympic Games; she withdrew from most of the events and competed only on the balance beam (where she won bronze).\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"the elite world\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"twisties\\\"during her vault\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"the team competition\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the term sounds light and fun, it's anything but-it could be super serious: Biles lost her air awareness; she could no longer sense where she was during a skill, which could cause injury or worse.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the term\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"her air awareness\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"a skill\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles thought her career was over.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an April 2024 interview on the podcastCall Her Daddy,Biles told host Alex Cooper that she thoughtThe world is going to hate meafter she walked off the competition floor and wondered if she would be allowed back into the US without the gold medal she felt was expected of her.\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2536, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"score\": 0.860757357501504, \"rank\": 0.1617647058823005, \"text\": \"Alex Cooper\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\"}, {\"begin\": 2687, \"end\": 2689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9957419300604237, \"rank\": 0.004275026452897043, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an April 2024 interview\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"the podcastCall Her Daddy\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"she thoughtThe world\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"meafter\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition floor\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The combination of competing in a huge event during a global pandemic and the repressed trauma from the Larry Nassar sexual abuse scandal just \\\"cracked\\\" her, as shetold Cooper.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2847, \"end\": 2859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"score\": 0.9999813659186598, \"rank\": 1.863442871288712e-05, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The combination\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge event\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"a global pandemic\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"the repressed trauma\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"Cooper\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Tokyo Games, Biles took time off to prioritize her mental health, including throughweekly therapy sessions, and continues to speak out about the importance of doing so-something that's definitely beneficial to the latest crop of gymnasts.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2959}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"throughweekly therapy sessions\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"so-something\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest crop\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, she has gained a reputation as a supportive teammate, particularly to the younger gymnasts with whom she trains at World Champions Centre, the Texas gym owned by her family, and who grew up idolizing her.\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3322, \"end\": 3327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns_football\", \"score\": 0.6828082197885087, \"rank\": 0.4645400347407683, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns_football\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"a reputation\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"a supportive teammate\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"the younger gymnasts\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3269}, {\"ngram\": \"World Champions Centre\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles turned 27 this year and is the oldest American gymnast headed to the Olympics since the 1950s.\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3429, \"end\": 3437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9476832298048693, \"rank\": 0.05493262613365673, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3390}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with age comes wisdom and experience: \\\"I use the phrase, 'aging like fine wine,'\\\" Biles said toUSA Todayafter her victory at US nationals.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3615, \"end\": 3617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9957419300604237, \"rank\": 0.004275026452897043, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"wisdom\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3511}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"fine wine\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"her victory\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going into Paris, Biles is proving that we are in the new era of American gymnastics-one in which health and safety is prioritized, and athletes can compete well into their 20s as a result-and we will be tuning in to watch it.\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3640, \"end\": 3645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1482261874467196e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3694, \"end\": 3702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9476832298048693, \"rank\": 0.05493262613365673, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3652}, {\"ngram\": \"the new era\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"health\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3733}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3744}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3773}, {\"ngram\": \"their 20s\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee went from veritable obscurity to overnight fame when won the all-around competition at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3857, \"end\": 3860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.618533281801537e-13, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"veritable obscurity\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"overnight fame\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around competition\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That made herthe first Asian American all-around Olympic champion; perhaps more importantly, she was the first Olympian, period, from the close-knit Hmong American community that is largely based in Lee's home state, Minnesota.\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 4192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3988, \"end\": 4002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4467949378840162e-21, \"text\": \"Asian American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 3988, \"end\": 4002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4467949378840162e-21, \"text\": \"Asian American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 4076, \"end\": 4084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.458814634743977e-15, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 4114, \"end\": 4128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hmong_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hmong American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hmong_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hmong_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 4164, \"end\": 4167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.618533281801537e-13, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 4182, \"end\": 4191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_ice_hockey\", \"score\": 0.5223316365945941, \"rank\": 0.6305297692325