rns_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns_football\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 6742, \"to\": 6748}, {\"ngram\": \"her junior year\", \"from\": 6758, \"to\": 6773}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Games\", \"from\": 6792, \"to\": 6808}, {\"ngram\": \"full-time\", \"from\": 6818, \"to\": 6827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a risk-at one point, Chiles said she was asked to alter her floor routine, since an official did not think her NCAA-style routine, set to '90s hip-hop music, would score well internationally, as she toldGymCastic.\", \"from\": 6838, \"to\": 7058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a risk\", \"from\": 6845, \"to\": 6851}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 6855, \"to\": 6864}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 6866, \"to\": 6872}, {\"ngram\": \"her floor routine\", \"from\": 6901, \"to\": 6918}, {\"ngram\": \"an official\", \"from\": 6926, \"to\": 6937}, {\"ngram\": \"her NCAA-style routine\", \"from\": 6952, \"to\": 6974}, {\"ngram\": \"90s\", \"from\": 6984, \"to\": 6987}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop music\", \"from\": 6988, \"to\": 7001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, however, Chiles was able to reach a performance compromise-\\\"I changed it where I could still enjoy having the college fun Jordan with the elite Jordan,\\\" as she told GymCastic, and make the Olympic team.\", \"from\": 7060, \"to\": 7274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7216, \"end\": 7222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999993468256748, \"rank\": 6.51432065725886e-07, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 7081, \"to\": 7087}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance\", \"from\": 7106, \"to\": 7119}, {\"ngram\": \"compromise-\\\"I\", \"from\": 7120, \"to\": 7133}, {\"ngram\": \"the college fun\", \"from\": 7178, \"to\": 7193}, {\"ngram\": \"GymCastic\", \"from\": 7237, \"to\": 7246}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team\", \"from\": 7257, \"to\": 7273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, her enthusiasm, consistency-and ability to hype up her teammatesto help them go all-out-will be a major asset to the US team's quest for gold.\", \"from\": 7275, \"to\": 7427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7278, \"end\": 7283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1482261874467196e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 7402, \"end\": 7404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9957419300604237, \"rank\": 0.004275026452897043, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her enthusiasm\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7299}, {\"ngram\": \"consistency\", \"from\": 7301, \"to\": 7312}, {\"ngram\": \"ability\", \"from\": 7317, \"to\": 7324}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammatesto\", \"from\": 7336, \"to\": 7351}, {\"ngram\": \"a major asset\", \"from\": 7381, \"to\": 7394}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 7422, \"to\": 7426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Chiles is the dynamic cheerleader of the Paris team, Jade Carey is its quiet, steady guiding force.\", \"from\": 7429, \"to\": 7531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7473, \"end\": 7478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1482261874467196e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 7485, \"end\": 7495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 7432, \"to\": 7438}, {\"ngram\": \"the dynamic cheerleader\", \"from\": 7442, \"to\": 7465}, {\"ngram\": \"its quiet, steady guiding force\", \"from\": 7499, \"to\": 7530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But like Chiles, she had her own dramatic gymnastics trajectory: In 2016, she was a high-level college recruit who had never considered the elite side of the sport; by 2021, she was an Olympic gold medalist.\", \"from\": 7532, \"to\": 7739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 7541, \"to\": 7547}, {\"ngram\": \"her own dramatic gymnastics trajectory\", \"from\": 7557, \"to\": 7595}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-level college recruit\", \"from\": 7614, \"to\": 7642}, {\"ngram\": \"the elite side\", \"from\": 7668, \"to\": 7682}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 7686, \"to\": 7695}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold medalist\", \"from\": 7714, \"to\": 7738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You probably would not call her flashy, but when you watch her floor routine, you can not help but notice she throws the most difficult acrobatic skills in the world this side of Biles.\", \"from\": 7740, \"to\": 7925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her floor routine\", \"from\": 7799, \"to\": 7816}, {\"ngram\": \"the most difficult acrobatic skills\", \"from\": 7857, \"to\": 7892}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 7896, \"to\": 7905}, {\"ngram\": \"this side\", \"from\": 7906, \"to\": 7915}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 7919, \"to\": 7924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She charted her own path to the Tokyo Olympics, competing at World Cups until she nabbed an individual spot for the US.\", \"from\": 7927, \"to\": 8046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8043, \"end\": 8045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9957419300604237, \"rank\": 0.004275026452897043, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own path\", \"from\": 7939, \"to\": 7951}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 7955, \"to\": 7973}, {\"ngram\": \"World Cups\", \"from\": 7988, \"to\": 7998}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual spot\", \"from\": 8016, \"to\": 8034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she was on her own, unable to share in the team medal there.\", \"from\": 8047, \"to\": 8111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team medal\", \"from\": 8090, \"to\": 8104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now at her second Games, she will be getting the full experience as a full-fledged part of the five-woman team in Paris.\", \"from\": 8112, \"to\": 8232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8226, \"end\": 8231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1482261874467196e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her second Games\", \"from\": 8119, \"to\": 8135}, {\"ngram\": \"the full experience\", \"from\": 8157, \"to\": 8176}, {\"ngram\": \"a full-fledged part\", \"from\": 8180, \"to\": 8199}, {\"ngram\": \"the five-woman team\", \"from\": 8203, \"to\": 8222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's key, because-if her performance as part of Oregon State's gymnastics squad over the last three years is any indication-she thrives as part of a close-knit team.\", \"from\": 8234, \"to\": 8401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8284, \"end\": 8290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.76273625528119, \"rank\": 0.3110632355897749, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 8257, \"to\": 8272}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 8276, \"to\": 8280}, {\"ngram\": \"the last three years\", \"from\": 8321, \"to\": 8341}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 8375, \"to\": 8379}, {\"ngram\": \"a close-knit team\", \"from\": 8383, \"to\": 8400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike Lee, who left college gymnastics altogether, and Chiles, who deferred a year to train for the Olympics, Carey competed for the Beavers all season, building on the consistency and calmness under pressure that are her hallmarks in the elite world.\", \"from\": 8402, \"to\": 8654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8409, \"end\": 8412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.618533281801537e-13, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 8513, \"end\": 8518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.864173933280808e-35, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"college gymnastics\", \"from\": 8423, \"to\": 8441}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 8458, \"to\": 8464}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 8479, \"to\": 8485}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 8499, \"to\": 8511}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beavers\", \"from\": 8532, \"to\": 8543}, {\"ngram\": \"the consistency\", \"from\": 8568, \"to\": 8583}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 8603, \"to\": 8611}, {\"ngram\": \"her hallmarks\", \"from\": 8621, \"to\": 8634}, {\"ngram\": \"the elite world\", \"from\": 8638, \"to\": 8653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But make no mistake: As stellar a teammate as she's sure to be, Carey probably has some individual goals in mind too.\", \"from\": 8656, \"to\": 8773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8720, \"end\": 8725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.864173933280808e-35, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no mistake\", \"from\": 8665, \"to\": 8675}, {\"ngram\": \"some individual goals\", \"from\": 8739, \"to\": 8760}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 8764, \"to\": 8768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We bet she's coming for that vault medal she missed in Tokyo, and she's got a floor medal to defend as well.\", \"from\": 8774, \"to\": 8882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8829, \"end\": 8834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9421511614332093, \"rank\": 0.06140080374676294, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that vault medal\", \"from\": 8798, \"to\": 8814}, {\"ngram\": \"a floor medal\", \"from\": 8850, \"to\": 8863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hezly Rivera was this year's wild card.\", \"from\": 8884, \"to\": 8923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8890, \"end\": 8896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999913858644449, \"rank\": 8.61420972628679e-06, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this year's wild card\", \"from\": 8901, \"to\": 8922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first-year senior elite competitor with just a few big meets under her belt showed a newfound consistency coupled with her usual excellent execution-and a few well-placed big skills-to nudge her way onto the Paris team.\", \"from\": 8924, \"to\": 9147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9136, \"end\": 9141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1482261874467196e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first-year senior elite competitor\", \"from\": 8924, \"to\": 8962}, {\"ngram\": \"just a few big meets\", \"from\": 8968, \"to\": 8988}, {\"ngram\": \"her belt\", \"from\": 8995, \"to\": 9003}, {\"ngram\": \"a newfound consistency\", \"from\": 9011, \"to\": 9033}, {\"ngram\": \"her usual excellent execution\", \"from\": 9047, \"to\": 9076}, {\"ngram\": \"a few well-placed big skills\", \"from\": 9081, \"to\": 9109}, {\"ngram\": \"her way\", \"from\": 9119, \"to\": 9126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rivera toldthe Olympic Channelthat she treated the Trials like just another meet.\", \"from\": 9148, \"to\": 9229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9148, \"end\": 9154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999913858644449, \"rank\": 8.61420972628679e-06, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 9163, \"to\": 9170}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trials\", \"from\": 9195, \"to\": 9205}, {\"ngram\": \"just another meet\", \"from\": 9211, \"to\": 9228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it probably would have been just that for her until several frontrunne